    The main class which extends the javafx.application.Application class.
    MainController
    A GUI class which allows user to select ordering coffee, ordering donuts, viewing their basket, and viewing store orders.
    MenuItem
    This is the superclass of all menu items, such as donuts and coffee.
    Order
    An instance of this class has a unique order number and keeps the list of menu items added by the user (called orders).
    OrderingBasketController
    A GUI class which allows user to view their current order (basket), remove any items from the basket, and place their order
    OrderingCoffeeController
    A GUI class which allows user to order coffee
    OrderingDonutsController
    A GUI class which allows user to order donuts
    StoreOrders
    An instance of this class keeps a list of all orders placed
    StoreOrdersController
    A GUI class which allows user to view all orders that have been placed, cancel any orders, and export order to text file.
